# DatePicker

The date picker lets users select a single date (a day) or a date range (a week) with an interface that looks like a calendar and is just as straightforward to use.
Please note that for handheld devices, a native `<input type="date">` tag is used, so props related to hiding and showing the
calendar or text field do not work, and the "value" property of the input tag is always in short ISO format.

## Installation & Import

```bash
yarn add @ids-ts/date-picker
```

```tsx
import { DatePicker, DatePickerComponent } from '@ids-ts/date-picker';
```

## Props API

| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `automationId` | `string` | No | Automation test identifier. |
| `data-drpIndex` | `'start' \| 'end'` | No | Index for date range picker styling. |
| `announcementMinDate` | `string` | No | Used to announce min date via screen reader. |
| `announcementMaxDate` | `string` | No | Used to announce max date via screen reader. |
| `announcementCurrentDate` | `string` | No | Used to announce current date via screen reader. |
| `currentDate` | `string` | No | The date DatePicker will assume is today. Defaults to today. |
| `currentDateTitle` | `string` | No | Accessible title for the current date. |
| `dateFormat` | `string` | Yes | Date format string (e.g., `'MM/DD/YYYY'`). |
| `dayOfWeekLabels` | `string[]` | Yes | Array of abbreviated weekday labels. |
| `fullDayOfWeekLabels` | `string[]` | No | Array of full weekday names for accessibility. |
| `disabled` | `boolean` | No | Disables the date input when true. |
| `footerTextClass` | `string` | No | Class applied to footer text (validation and helper). |
| `hasWeightedLabel` | `boolean` | No | Makes the label bold when true. |
| `helperText` | `string` | No | Helper text displayed below the input. |
| `readOnly` | `boolean` | No | Makes the input read-only when true. |
| `enableAutoFormatting` | `boolean` | No | Enables auto-formatting of the text field input. |
| `endingDate` | `string \| DateWrapper` | No | End date for range pickers. |
| `id` | `string` | No | ID of the root container. |
| `errorText` | `string` | No | Error message displayed below the input. |
| `isMobile` | `boolean` | No | Override for mobile detection (used for testing). |
| `isRangePicker` | `boolean` | No | Used by DateRangePicker for styling. |
| `isMonthYearPicker` | `boolean` | No | Used by month/year picker variant. |
| `label` | `string` | No | Label for the date input field. |
| `maxDate` | `string \| DateWrapper` | No | Maximum selectable date. |
| `minDate` | `string \| DateWrapper` | No | Minimum selectable date. |
| `monthLabels` | `string[]` | Yes | Array of month name labels. |
| `name` | `string` | No | Name attribute for the input. |
| `nextMonthAriaLabel` | `string` | Yes | Accessible label for the next month button. |
| `previousMonthAriaLabel` | `string` | Yes | Accessible label for the previous month button. |
| `onFocus` | `React.FocusEventHandler` | No | Called when the input receives focus. |
| `onBlur` | `React.FocusEventHandler` | No | Called when the input loses focus. |
| `onChange` | `(event: ChangeEventType) => void` | No | Called when the selected date changes. |
| `onCalendarOpen` | `() => void` | No | Called when the calendar opens. |
| `onCalendarClose` | `() => void` | No | Called when the calendar closes. |
| `placeholder` | `string` | No | Placeholder text for the input. |
| `preventCalendarOverflow` | `PreventOverflow` | No | Controls calendar overflow behavior. |
| `renderTooltip` | `RenderTooltipType` | No | Custom tooltip renderer. |
| `showCalendar` | `boolean` | No | Controls calendar open/closed state. |
| `size` | `TextFieldProps['size']` | No | Size of the date picker text field. |
| `startingDate` | `string \| DateWrapper` | No | Start date for range pickers. |
| `calendarPositionStyle` | `React.CSSProperties` | No | Additional styles for the calendar position node. |
| `validationError` | `boolean` | No | Shows error state styling when true. |
| `warningText` | `string` | No | Warning message displayed below the input. |
| `useDoubleCalendar` | `boolean` | No | Shows two calendar months side by side. |
| `value` | `string \| DateWrapper` | Yes | Selected date value. |
| `displayStrikeOutsideOfMinMaxRange` | `boolean` | No | Strikes through dates outside min/max range. |
| `enableMonthYearQuickSelect` | `boolean` | No | Enables month and year quick select dropdowns. |
| `quickSelectMinYear` | `number` | No | Minimum year for the quick select dropdown. |
| `quickSelectMaxYear` | `number` | No | Maximum year for the quick select dropdown. |
| `abbreviatedDateFormat` | `string` | No | Date format abbreviation for different locales. |

